<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Asks Norway To Secure International Aid </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat Asks Norway To Secure International Aid </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0706213694 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 7 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0706213694 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Brother President Yasir 'Arafat had today a 
telephone conversation with the Mr. Godal, the Norwegian foreign 
minister. 
  The conversation dealt with the latest development in the 
Palestinian-Israeli peace process and the means for bolstering 
it by starting the rebuilding process as soon as possible. 
  They also talked about the International Coordination 
Committee of the donor-countries and the need to fulfill its 
pledges by giving monies to the Palestinian authority in order 
that the latter would meet its development and rebuilding 
pledges in the self rule areas. 

