<H3> <TI>   PLO Reaches Fuel Supply Agreement With Egypt </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PLO Reaches Fuel Supply Agreement With Egypt </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0606124894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1000 GMT 6 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0606124894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The PLO is reported to have reached agreement with 
Egypt on the regular supply of fuel and gas to the self-rule 
areas. A Qol Yisra'el reporter says within the next few days the 
first Egyptian tanker will anchor off Gaza to supply fuel to the 
strip. In the strip, fuel prices have already gone down by 10 
percent when compared with Israeli prices. 

</TEXT>

