<H3> <TI>   Shin Bet Uncovers Attempt To Assassinate Al-Rujub </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shin Bet Uncovers Attempt To Assassinate Al-Rujub </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0706181794 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network in 
Hebrew 1700 GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0706181794 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Shin Bet several days ago uncovered an 
assassination attempt against Jibril al-Rujub, head of the 
Palestinian preventive security service. Al-Rujub, who was in 
Tulkarm that day, was informed he had better cancel a planned 
visit to Nabulus because he can expect an unpleasant surprise 
there. 
  The tension between the Palestinian police and Hamas 
[Islamic 
Resistance Movement] in the Gaza and Jericho autonomy areas is 
increasing. 

</TEXT>

