<H3> <TI>   YSP Member Holds Town Meeting After Shelling </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    YSP Member Holds Town Meeting After Shelling </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   EA0906100594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network 
in English 1600 GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA0906100594 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network 
in English 1600 GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=105> English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Dr. Sayf Sayil Khalid, Politburo member and member 
of the Central Committee of the Yemeni Socialist Party [YSP], 
met today with the citizens of the town of Dar Sa'd following 
the haphazard artillery shelling launched from the Sanaa regime, 
which targeted the populated living quarters in the town of Dar 
Sa'd. Some families and innocent children were victims of this 
shelling. Dr. Sayf Sayil praised the high morale of the citizens 
and their persistence and readiness to resist in the face of the 
conspirators on the security, stability, and welfare of the 
people. 
  In this connection he called for the necessity of organizing 
the popular resistance to protect our beautiful city against the 
conspiracies of the enemies. He said: We will not allow Aden 
to be occupied, no matter what. He emphasized that the citizens 
of the capital, Aden, are considered to come from all the 
villages and regions of Yemen and that going to the resistance 
fronts reflects the real pattern of unity of the sons of the 
Yemeni people. 
  In the context of his talk with the citizens of the sons of 
Dar Sa'd, Dr. Sayf Sayil indicated that the inhabitants, men and 
women, all of them joined the Armed Forces to defend Aden. He 
said that this mad war had targeted the Yemeni people, whether 
on a human, economic or military scale. The instigators and 
causers of this war will be cursed by history, he said, adding 
that the will of the people is stronger than the will of the 
crazy adventurous rulers. Victory will be only with the people, 
he said. 

</TEXT>

