<H3> <TI>   German Parliamentary Delegation Arrives in Baghdad </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    German Parliamentary Delegation Arrives in Baghdad </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Confers With al-Sahhaf </H4>

<F P=102> JN0706192894 Baghdad INA in Arabic 1828 GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN0706192894 </F>
<F P=104>  Baghdad INA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Baghdad, 7 Jun (INA)--Foreign Minister Muhammad 
Sa'id al-Sahhaf met this evening with the visiting German 
parliamentary delegation, led by Dr. Hans Sterchen, chairman of 
the Bundestag Foreign Policy Committee. 
  The minister discussed with the guest delegation the 
negative 
impact of the unjust blockade imposed on Iraq. The blockade, he 
said, continues although Iraq met the obligations stated in UN 
resolutions. 
  The two sides exchanged views on several issues of mutual 
interest. Sterchen stressed eagerness to strengthen contacts 
between Iraq and Germany. 

</TEXT>

