  [Text] Baghdad, 7 Jun (INA)--Deputy Prime Minister Tariq 
'Aziz received today the visiting German parliamentary 
delegation led by Hans Sterchen, chairman of the Bundestag 
Foreign Policy Committee. 
  They discussed relations between Iraq and Germany and 
stressed the need to restore them to normalcy in order to serve 
national interests of both peoples and countries. The meeting 
also tackled Iraq's relations with the Security Council, as well 
as the need to lift the unjust blockade imposed on Iraq. 

</TEXT>

