<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Philippine Foreign Minister Roberto Romulo says he 
will positively recommend to his president Israel Aircraft 
Industries products, particularly Kfir planes. At the end of 
his visit he called on Israeli high-tech firms to establish 
production and marketing systems in the Philippines that could 
serve as a basis for all Southeast Asia. Romulo also said his 
country would be glad to help Israel in promoting relations with 
Muslim states in the area, whom he believed would establish full 
ties with Israel as the peace process advanced. 

