<F P=100> Syria </F>
<H3> <TI>   Al-Asad Meets With Lithuanian Envoy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Al-Asad Meets With Lithuanian Envoy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0906201594 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1815 GMT 9 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0906201594 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] His Excellency President Hafiz al-Asad received 
Lithuanian Parliament Speaker Cheslovas Yurshenas at the 
People's Palace at 1830 today. People's Assembly Speaker 
'Abd-al-Qadir Qaddurah attended the session. 
  Mr. Yurshenas conveyed a message from Lithuanian President 
Algirdas Brazauskas underscoring the importance of increased 
ties between the two countries. His excellency the president 
thanked the envoy and asked him to convey his greetings to the 
Lithuanian president. 
  Discussions during the meeting dealt with the Middle East 
and 
the Baltic. His excellency the president laid out to him the 
efforts being made to bring about a just and comprehensive peace 
to the region and the obstacles placed by Israel in the path of 
that objective. His excellency the president also clarified 
Syria's sound position on the peace process predicated on UN 
resolutions and international legitimacy. 
  Mr. Yurshenas said his country wholly supports the 
implementation of UN Security Council resolutions and the 
restitution of Syrian and other Arab territory. 

</TEXT>

