<F P=100> Libya </F>
<H3> <TI>   Airspace Opened To African Delegations' Aircraft </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Airspace Opened To African Delegations' Aircraft </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1106164694 Tripoli JANA in English 1635 GMT 11 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1106164694 </F>
<F P=104>  Tripoli JANA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tripoli, Al-Sayf [June] 11, JAMAHIRIYAH NEWS AGENCY 
-- JANA has learnt that Libya decided to open her national 
airspace to allow the transit of aircraft carrying delegations 
to the African summit conference which is due to start in Tunis 
on Monday. 

</TEXT>

