<F P=100> ISRAEL </F>
<H3> <TI>   Woman Killed by IDF During Ramallah Riots </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Woman Killed by IDF During Ramallah Riots </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1106132394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1300 GMT 11 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1106132394 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Siham 'Asawati, a 37-year-old resident of Ramallah, 
was killed this morning by shots fired by IDF [Israel Defense 
Forces] soldiers who were dispersing rioters in the center of 
the town. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports that the soldiers 
were dispersing stone throwers and rioters by shooting rubber 
bullets and using tear gas. The woman was seriously wounded in 
the head by a rubber bullet and taken to a Ramallah hospital, 
where she died of her wounds. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

